---
---
<div class="panel area-import-export import-export-center">
  <div class="iec-head">
    <div>
      <h2>📦 导入 / 导出中心</h2>
      <p class="iec-desc">统一处理世界书 JSON、快速回复 QR、香草 AI 角色卡、SillyTavern 角色卡和 PNG 头像 / 卡片。</p>
    </div>
    <span id="importAssetStatus" class="iec-status">等待导入</span>
  </div>

  <div class="iec-grid">
    <section class="iec-card ie-import-card">
      <div class="iec-card-head">
        <div>
          <h3>导入</h3>
          <p class="iec-card-desc">文件和粘贴都走同一个自动识别入口。</p>
        </div>
        <span class="iec-pill">AUTO</span>
      </div>

      <div class="iec-actions">
        <input type="file" id="importAssetInput" accept=".json,.png,application/json,image/png" />
        <button id="btnImportAssetFile" class="btn btn-fetch" type="button" style="margin:0;">选择文件导入</button>
        <button id="btnImportAssetText" class="btn btn-fetch" type="button" style="margin:0;">粘贴内容导入</button>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom:0;">
        <label>JSON / 卡片内容</label>
        <textarea id="importAssetText" class="iec-textarea" placeholder="粘贴世界书 JSON、快速回复 QR JSON、香草 AI 角色卡 JSON、SillyTavern 角色卡 JSON，或拖入 .json /.png 文件"></textarea>
      </div>

      <p class="iec-card-tip">PNG 文件会优先尝试读取卡片数据；没有 `chara` 的 PNG 会按纯头像处理。</p>
    </section>

    <section class="iec-card ie-export-card">
      <div class="iec-card-head">
        <div>
          <h3>导出</h3>
          <p class="iec-card-desc">先选格式，再导出对应文件。</p>
        </div>
        <span class="iec-pill ie-pill-export">EXPORT</span>
      </div>

      <div class="iec-export-row">
        <div class="export-menu-shell">
          <button id="btnExportMenu" class="btn btn-fetch ie-export-menu-btn" type="button">💾 导出格式</button>
          <div id="exportFormatMenu" class="export-format-menu" hidden>
            <button type="button" class="export-format-item" data-export-format="vanilla">香草 AI 角色卡</button>
            <button type="button" class="export-format-item" data-export-format="st">SillyTavern 角色卡</button>
            <button type="button" class="export-format-item" data-export-format="worldbook-md">世界书 md</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button id="btnExportPNG" class="btn btn-img" type="button" style="margin:0;">📸 导出 PNG</button>
      </div>

      <p class="iec-card-tip">空字段会保留 key，并补默认值，不会因为未编辑就消失。</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>

<style is:global>
  .import-export-center {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.12), transparent 28%),
      radial-gradient(circle at bottom left, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.12), transparent 30%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.96), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.88));
    border: 1px solid rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.18);
  }

  .iec-head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .iec-head h2 {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .iec-desc {
    margin: 6px 0 0;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .iec-status {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.18);
    color: #7dd3fc;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .iec-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.25fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .iec-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 14px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(71, 85, 105, 0.4);
    background: rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.45);
  }

  .iec-card-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .iec-card-head h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.96rem;
  }

  .iec-card-desc {
    margin: 4px 0 0;
    font-size: 0.73rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .iec-pill {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    color: #a5f3fc;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
    background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.08);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .iec-pill-export {
    color: #c4b5fd;
    border-color: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.24);
    background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
  }

  .iec-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .iec-actions input[type="file"] {
    display: none;
  }

  .iec-textarea {
    min-height: 92px;
    resize: vertical;
  }

  .iec-card-tip {
    margin: -4px 0 0;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: #64748b;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .iec-export-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .iec-export-menu-btn {
    min-width: 148px;
  }

  .export-menu-shell {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .export-format-menu {
    position: absolute;
    right: 0;
    top: calc(100% + 6px);
    z-index: 30;
    min-width: 172px;
    padding: 6px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.98);
    border: 1px solid rgba(71, 85, 105, 0.85);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .export-format-item {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
    text-align: left;
    border: 0;
    background: transparent;
    color: #e2e8f0;
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    line-height: 1.35;
    padding: 8px 10px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: inherit;
  }

  .export-format-item:hover {
    background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.12);
    color: #f8fafc;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .iec-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
